longBusinessSummary: Easy Technologies Inc. develops an Internet based platform in the online gaming area. It develops HouseTrivia.com, a platform that holds various trivia competitions. The company was formerly known as EasyMed Technologies Inc. and changed its name to Easy Technologies Inc. in January 2016. Easy Technologies Inc. was founded in 2005 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
